    <subfield code="y">00000 Schematic trajectory of a galactic CR reaccelerated by a relativistic jet (not in scale). The total acceleration due to the inductive electric field does not depend on the exact trajectory: a rotation $\gtrsim \pi/2$ around the jet magnetic field is sufficient for an energy gain of a factor of $\sim\Gamma^2$.</subfield>
